# Stage 07 ‚Äî merge (L2)

Finalizes the implementation cycle: integrates the `workspace_branch` rebased into `base_branch` (usually `main`), optionally opens a PR or creates a release tag. Decision "direct merge / PR / tag-only" is a human menu. After execution, the workspace automatically transitions to **stage 08 (feedback intake)** with `status: COMPLETED_AWAITING_HUMAN` ‚Äî workspace stays "alive" waiting for the human to return with feedback after real use of the project. Workspace ONLY closes (status `COMPLETED`) when stage 08 decides output A (close).

