## Gates

- **Human:** chooses A/B/C in the merge menu; confirms the merge-report at the end.
- **Automatic (CI):** pre-commit hook validates L1‚Üîoutputs atomicity and commit prefix `workspace/{{WORKSPACE}}`. Post-merge, CI of `base_branch` validates the integrated state.
- **Approval to transition:** human confirms merge-report; sub_stage becomes `07_completed` and status immediately transitions to `COMPLETED_AWAITING_HUMAN` (stage 08). `COMPLETED` is NOT set in this stage ‚Äî definitive close only in stage 08 output A.

## End of stage handoff (gate inline + auto-transition 07‚Üí08)

